risk_explanation: This is an insurance contract endorsement transferring obligations from Thrivent Life Insurance Company to Thrivent Financial for Lutherans and adding solvency-related member payment obligations. It does not include typical SaaS protections such as a liability cap, termination rights, or governing law in the provided text. The solvency impairment clause (extra payment within 60 days or indebtedness with 5% interest) increases financial exposure, creating moderate risk.
